Internet marketing, its importance and trends. Overview of different channels of internet marketing and their possibilities, incl homepage, social media, ads, blogs, e-mails etc. Creating strategy of internet marketing, including segmentation, target marketing and positioning. Consumer behavior in internet. SEO and its importance. Measurement and analytics of internet marketing.Objectives/eesmärkid:  The aim of the course is to introduce different opportunities of internet marketing including planning, methods and channels.Learning outcomes/õpiväljund:  Upon the completion of the course the student: 1) understands what internet marketing is and why it is important; 2) is familiar with and know how to implement different marketing activities in internet channels; 3) is able to plan marketing strategies in different internet channels; 4) understands the consumer behaviour in internet; 5) understands the importance of measurement and analytics of internet marketing for the companies.
